      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a premium, modern, and culturally rooted e-commerce website for PRITHVO, an Indian handicraft startup specializing in clay and pottery. The website will showcase handmade products, highlight artisan stories, emphasize sustainability, and provide a seamless online shopping experience."
