      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Homepage Content**: Displays a strong hero section with artisans at work, brand introduction, and featured products.\n- **View About Information**: Tells the story of Indian mitti, artisans, and heritage, reflecting brand values.\n- **View Product Listing**: Showcases clay products like pots, diyas, cookware, and decor items in a catalog format.\n- **Filter Products**: Allows users to filter products by category, type, or artisan.\n- **View Product Details**: Provides detailed information, images, and pricing for each individual product.\n- **View Artisan Listing**: Displays a list of featured craftsmen and their profiles.\n- **View Artisan Details**: Offers in-depth stories and journeys of individual artisans.\n- **View Sustainability Information**: Explains the brand's eco-friendly and handmade values.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Allows visitors to send inquiries and connect with the brand.",
